<style>
  body {
    font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
    color: #EEF2E6;
    background-color: #032615;
    height: 100vh;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .container.abstinence-goal {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    height: 100%;
    text-align: center; /* Add this line */
  }

  h1 {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  form {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 400px;
  }

  .submit-button {
    background-color: #EEF2E6;
    border: 1px solid #EEF2E6;
    border-radius: 5px;
    box-shadow: 2px 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    color: #032615;
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    display: inline-block;
    margin: 5px;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .submit-button:hover {
    background-color: #032615;
    color: #EEF2E6;
  }

  label {
    font-weight: bold;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  select {
    background-color: #EEF2E6;
    border-radius: 5px;
    border: 1px solid #032615;
    padding: 0.5rem;
    color: #032615;
    font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
  }

  .separator {
  border-top: 2px solid #EEF2E6;
  width: 100%;
  margin: 2rem 0;
  }
</style>

<div class="container abstinence-goal">
  <h1>Abstinence goal</h1>

  <div style="margin: 0 0.5rem;">
  Your abstinence goal is the initial length of time you want to go without watching porn. Setting short term aims gives you realistic goals which you can achieve. enna will support you as you work towards these goals, which you can change at any time.
  </div>

  <div class="separator"></div>

  <%= simple_form_for @abstinence_goal do |f| %>
    <%= f.input :length, label: "Number of days: ", collection: ["1", "3", "5", "7", "14"], input_html: { class: 'custom-select' } %>
    
    <%= f.submit value="Confirm goal", class: "submit-button", style: "margin-top: 10px;" %>
  <% end %>

 
</div>
